9
00:01:32.573 --> 00:01:34.533
<i>ia hampir mustahil.</i>

10
00:01:35.826 --> 00:01:37.244
<i>Hampir separuh daripada
anak-anak beruang</i>


11
00:01:37.286 --> 00:01:39.538
