21
00:02:15.157 --> 00:02:16.784
<i>Tetapi kini ia berasa lapar,</i>

22
00:02:16.867 --> 00:02:18.494
<i>dan jika ia tak cepat makan,</i>

23
00:02:18.577 --> 00:02:20.996
